args.code:
import PyPDF2

pdf_path = '/workspace/benchmark/datasets/30-ERGO/ERGO/paper.pdf'
with open(pdf_path, 'rb') as f:
    reader = PyPDF2.PdfReader(f)
    num_pages = len(reader.pages)
    text = ''
    for i in range(num_pages):
        text += reader.pages[i].extract_text() + '\n'

# Print the first 2000 characters to inspect for the loss function
print(text[:2000])
